      • MediaDiscoverer

        public MediaDiscoverer(LibVLC libVLC,
                       java.lang.String name)
        Create a MediaDiscover.
        パラメータ:
        libVLC - a valid LibVLC
        name - Name of the vlc service discovery ("dsm", "upnp", "bonjour"...).

    • メソッドの詳細

      • start

        public boolean start()
        Starts the discovery. This MediaDiscoverer should be alive (not released).
        戻り値:
        true the service is started

      • stop

        public void stop()
        Stops the discovery. This MediaDiscoverer should be alive (not released). (You can also call to stop the discovery directly.

      • setEventListener

        public void setEventListener(MediaDiscoverer.EventListener listener)

        戻り値:

      • getMediaList

        public MediaList getMediaList()
        Get the MediaList associated with the MediaDiscoverer. This MediaDiscoverer should be alive (not released).
        戻り値:
        MediaList. This MediaList should be released with release().

      • onReleaseNative

        protected void onReleaseNative()
        Called when native object is released (refcount is 0). This is where you must release native resources.

      • list

        Get media discoverers by category

      • isReleased

        public boolean isReleased()
        Returns true if native object is released

      • retain

        public final boolean retain()
        Increment internal ref count of the native object.
        戻り値:
        true if media is retained

      • release

        public final void release()
        Release the native object if ref count is 1. After this call, native calls are not possible anymore. You can still call others methods to retrieve cached values. For example: if you parse, then release a media, you'll still be able to retrieve all Metas or Tracks infos.

      • finalize

        パラメータ:

      • setEventListener

        protected void setEventListener(VLCEvent.Listener<T> listener,
                                android.os.Handler handler)
        Set an event listener and an executor Handler
        パラメータ:
        listener - see VLCEvent.Listener
        handler - Handler in which events are sent. If null, a handler will be created running on the main thread
